<h2>📬 New Contact Form Submission</h2>

<p>A new contact form has been submitted on the Rose des Vins website and requires your attention.</p>

<div class="success">
    <p><strong>New Application Received</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="credentials">
    <h3>👤 Contact Information</h3>
    <div class="field">
        <strong>Full Name:</strong> <span>{{fullName}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
        <strong>Email:</strong> <span>{{email}}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
        <strong>Domain:</strong> <span>{{domain}}</span>
    </div>
    {{#if message}}
    <div class="field" style="margin-top: 16px;">
        <strong>Message:</strong>
        <div style="margin-top: 8px; padding: 12px; background-color: #f8faf9; border-radius: 6px; font-style: italic; color: #4a5568;">
            "{{message}}"
        </div>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
</div>

<div class="highlight">
    <p><strong>⚡ Action Required:</strong> Please review this application and decide whether to approve or reject the membership request.</p>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{adminPanelUrl}}" class="button">
        🔍 Review in Admin Panel
    </a>
</p>

<p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
<ul style="color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.8;">
    <li>📝 Review the applicant's information</li>
    <li>✅ Approve to send welcome email with credentials</li>
    <li>❌ Reject to send polite rejection notification</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 30px;">
    <em style="color: #3A7B59;">Rose des Vins Admin System</em>
</p>
